      "text": "package.json\n  React 18, Next.js 14.2.14\n  @supabase/ssr, next-themes\n  PostHog analytics\n  remark-gfm, react-markdown\n\ntailwind.config.ts  \u2014 custom color tokens\ntsconfig.json       \u2014 strict mode, path aliases\npostcss.config.js   \u2014 Tailwind pipeline\n\nEnv vars (Vercel)\n  NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL\n  NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL\n  NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY\n\nAnalytics events tracked\n  search_submitted\n  citation_clicked\n  conversation_started\n  survey_response_submitted",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "package.json\n  React 18, Next.js 14.2.14\n  @supabase/ssr, next-themes\n  PostHog analytics\n  remark-gfm, react-markdown\n\ntailwind.config.ts  \u2014 custom color tokens\ntsconfig.json       \u2014 strict mode, path aliases\npostcss.config.js   \u2014 Tailwind pipeline\n\nEnv vars (Vercel)\n  NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL\n  NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL\n  NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY\n\nAnalytics events tracked\n  search_submitted\n  citation_clicked\n  conversation_started\n  survey_response_submitted",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
