      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "index.tsx         \u2014 Landing: Sign up / Log in\nregister.tsx      \u2014 Name, email, password\n                    Supabase signUp()\nphone.tsx         \u2014 Country code + phone number\nverify.tsx        \u2014 Cadre selection:\n                    \u00b7 Medical Practitioner\n                    \u00b7 Clinical Officer\n                    \u00b7 Dental Practitioner\n                    \u00b7 Intern\n                    + registration number\nspecialty.tsx     \u2014 Select specialties\n                    (filtered by cadre, max 3)\nrotation.tsx      \u2014 Rotation picker (Intern only)\nlogin.tsx         \u2014 Sign-in (Supabase signIn)\nforgot-password   \u2014 Reset email flow\nreset-password    \u2014 Confirm new password\ntrial-ask.tsx     \u2014 Anonymous query before auth\nverify-test.tsx   \u2014 Onboarding gate check\n\nStack nav: slide_from_right + swipe-back\nAuth listener in _layout.tsx\nDeep links: qwiva:// schema",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "index.tsx         \u2014 Landing: Sign up / Log in\nregister.tsx      \u2014 Name, email, password\n                    Supabase signUp()\nphone.tsx         \u2014 Country code + phone number\nverify.tsx        \u2014 Cadre selection:\n                    \u00b7 Medical Practitioner\n                    \u00b7 Clinical Officer\n                    \u00b7 Dental Practitioner\n                    \u00b7 Intern\n                    + registration number\nspecialty.tsx     \u2014 Select specialties\n                    (filtered by cadre, max 3)\nrotation.tsx      \u2014 Rotation picker (Intern only)\nlogin.tsx         \u2014 Sign-in (Supabase signIn)\nforgot-password   \u2014 Reset email flow\nreset-password    \u2014 Confirm new password\ntrial-ask.tsx     \u2014 Anonymous query before auth\nverify-test.tsx   \u2014 Onboarding gate check\n\nStack nav: slide_from_right + swipe-back\nAuth listener in _layout.tsx\nDeep links: qwiva:// schema",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
