      "text": "ask.tsx\n  Query interface\n  Streaming RAG answers\n  Suggestion chips\n  Mode selector (header)\n\nfeed.tsx\n  Community posts\n  Evidence sharing\n  Likes + comments\n\nlearn.tsx\n  CPD / CME modules\n  Learning tracks\n\npulse.tsx\n  Stats + leaderboard\n  XP, streaks, tiers\n\nme.tsx\n  Profile + tier\n  XP display\n\ncase.tsx  (root route)\n  Clinical MCQ game\n\nTab bar\n  BlurView on iOS\n  Opaque on Android\n\nFonts loaded in _layout.tsx\n  Lora, Gotham\n  JetBrains Mono, Gilroy",
