      "text": "ui/Button.tsx\n  Variants: primary \u00b7 navy\n            ghost \u00b7 danger \u00b7 outline\n  Sizes: sm \u00b7 md \u00b7 lg\n  Loading state spinner\n\nui/Badge.tsx\n  9 semantic variants:\n  success/warning/danger\n  info/tier/specialty\n\nui/Card.tsx\n  bgElevated surface\n  Radii.card, optional padding\n\nui/Input.tsx\n  text / numeric modes\n  Purple border on focus\n  Label + hint props\n\nui/QwivaLogo.tsx\n  2\u00d72 SVG grid\n  Navy/Purple/Lilac/Pink\n\nui/Skeleton.tsx\n  Shimmer loader\n  Reanimated 4.1.1\n  (no LinearGradient dep)\n\nsidebar/Sidebar.tsx\nsidebar/SidebarShell.tsx\nsheets/AddToChatSheet\nheader/ModeSelector",
