      "updated": 1745700000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "colors.ts\n  navy    #0B1F3A  primary brand\n  purple  #6B3FA0  AI / accent\n  lilac   #C4A8E0  soft UI\n  pink    #F2A7BB  decorative ONLY\n    (never interactive elements)\n\n  Surfaces\n    bgBase / bgElevated / bgOverlay\n  Text\n    textPrimary / textSecondary\n    textDisabled / textInverse\n  Semantic\n    success / warning / danger / info\n  Gamification\n    xpGold, streakFire\n    heartRed, tier colors\n\nspacing.ts\n  Scale s1(4px) \u2013 s16(64px)\n  Radii\n    chip \u00b7 button \u00b7 card\n    sheet \u00b7 hero \u00b7 pill\n\ntypography.ts\n  Lora        display headers\n  Gotham      sans body\n  Gilroy      landing only\n  JetBrains   data / mono\n\nresponseModes.ts\n  adaptive thinking\n  quick answer",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "colors.ts\n  navy    #0B1F3A  primary brand\n  purple  #6B3FA0  AI / accent\n  lilac   #C4A8E0  soft UI\n  pink    #F2A7BB  decorative ONLY\n    (never interactive elements)\n\n  Surfaces\n    bgBase / bgElevated / bgOverlay\n  Text\n    textPrimary / textSecondary\n    textDisabled / textInverse\n  Semantic\n    success / warning / danger / info\n  Gamification\n    xpGold, streakFire\n    heartRed, tier colors\n\nspacing.ts\n  Scale s1(4px) \u2013 s16(64px)\n  Radii\n    chip \u00b7 button \u00b7 card\n    sheet \u00b7 hero \u00b7 pill\n\ntypography.ts\n  Lora        display headers\n  Gotham      sans body\n  Gilroy      landing only\n  JetBrains   data / mono\n\nresponseModes.ts\n  adaptive thinking\n  quick answer",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
