      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1745700000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Calls RAG internals directly\n(not via HTTP \u2014 avoids\n network latency noise)\n\nPer-stage latency capture\n  embed_ms\n  retrieve_ms\n    \u251c vector_ms\n    \u2514 fts_ms\n  rerank_ms\n  ttft_ms  (time to first token)\n  total_ms\n\nOutput per question\n  answer text\n  citations list\n  retrieved chunks\n  evidence_grade\n  latency breakdown",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Calls RAG internals directly\n(not via HTTP \u2014 avoids\n network latency noise)\n\nPer-stage latency capture\n  embed_ms\n  retrieve_ms\n    \u251c vector_ms\n    \u2514 fts_ms\n  rerank_ms\n  ttft_ms  (time to first token)\n  total_ms\n\nOutput per question\n  answer text\n  citations list\n  retrieved chunks\n  evidence_grade\n  latency breakdown",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
