      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1745700000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "latency.py                       clinical.py\n  p50 / p95 / p99                  citation_rate\n  per-stage breakdown              source_coverage\n                                   unique guidelines cited\n\nragas_runner.py  (LLM judge via NVIDIA hub)\n  faithfulness          answer is grounded in retrieved context\n  answer_relevancy      answer actually addresses the question\n  context_precision     retrieved chunks are relevant\n  context_recall        relevant chunks were retrieved\n\ndeepeval_runner.py  (LLM judge via NVIDIA hub)\n  HallucinationMetric   detects invented facts not in context\n  ContextualPrecision   retrieved context is on-topic\n  ContextualRecall      context covers the expected answer",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "latency.py                       clinical.py\n  p50 / p95 / p99                  citation_rate\n  per-stage breakdown              source_coverage\n                                   unique guidelines cited\n\nragas_runner.py  (LLM judge via NVIDIA hub)\n  faithfulness          answer is grounded in retrieved context\n  answer_relevancy      answer actually addresses the question\n  context_precision     retrieved chunks are relevant\n  context_recall        relevant chunks were retrieved\n\ndeepeval_runner.py  (LLM judge via NVIDIA hub)\n  HallucinationMetric   detects invented facts not in context\n  ContextualPrecision   retrieved context is on-topic\n  ContextualRecall      context covers the expected answer",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
