      "text": "Dev: Expo Go SDK 54\n  iPhone limited by App Store\n\nProd: EAS cloud build\n  iOS App Store\n  Android Play Store\n\nDeep link scheme: qwiva://\n\nPhase: pre-launch\n  Expo Go + TestFlight",
