    {
      "id": "llm_anth_t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 28,
      "y": 6688,
      "width": 490,
      "height": 394,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#334155",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 71824,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1745800000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6\n(direct, not via Bedrock)\n\nROLE\n  Main answer generation\n  Both RAG + chat modes\n\nWhy direct?\n  Saves ~300ms TTFT vs\n  NVIDIA\u2192Bedrock route\n  Enables prompt caching\n\nPrompt caching\n  System prompt marked\n  cache_control: ephemeral\n  ~5min TTL \u00b7 big TTFT win\n  on follow-up queries\n\nStream=True\n  yields content tokens\n  via litellm.acompletion()\n\nAuth: ANTHROPIC_API_KEY",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6\n(direct, not via Bedrock)\n\nROLE\n  Main answer generation\n  Both RAG + chat modes\n\nWhy direct?\n  Saves ~300ms TTFT vs\n  NVIDIA\u2192Bedrock route\n  Enables prompt caching\n\nPrompt caching\n  System prompt marked\n  cache_control: ephemeral\n  ~5min TTL \u00b7 big TTFT win\n  on follow-up queries\n\nStream=True\n  yields content tokens\n  via litellm.acompletion()\n\nAuth: ANTHROPIC_API_KEY",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
