      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1745800000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "groq/llama-3.3-70b-versatile\n(LPU inference)\n\nROLES (3 fast paths)\n  classify (rag vs chat)\n  expand_query for short\n    follow-ups (\u22646 words)\n  generate title for new\n    conversations\n  generate suggestions\n    (currently disabled)\n\nLatency target\n  ~50\u2013150ms vs ~1100ms\n  on NVIDIA\u2192Bedrock route\n\nmax_tokens=5 for classify\n  (binary output only)\n\nAuth: GROQ_API_KEY",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "groq/llama-3.3-70b-versatile\n(LPU inference)\n\nROLES (3 fast paths)\n  classify (rag vs chat)\n  expand_query for short\n    follow-ups (\u22646 words)\n  generate title for new\n    conversations\n  generate suggestions\n    (currently disabled)\n\nLatency target\n  ~50\u2013150ms vs ~1100ms\n  on NVIDIA\u2192Bedrock route\n\nmax_tokens=5 for classify\n  (binary output only)\n\nAuth: GROQ_API_KEY",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
