    {
      "id": "llm_oai_t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1582,
      "y": 6688,
      "width": 490,
      "height": 394,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#334155",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 24522,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1745800000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Embeddings (direct)\ntext-embedding-3-large\n@ 1536 dimensions\n\nROLE\n  Embed query for vector\n  search \u00b7 matches model\n  used during ingestion\n\nWhy 1536 dims?\n  Matryoshka truncation\n  matches both:\n    pdf-pipeline output\n    pmc_oa_ingest output\n  Different model = garbage\n  vector search results\n\nDirect (not NVIDIA hub)\n  -3-large not available on\n  the NVIDIA inference hub\n\nAuth: OPENAI_API_KEY",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Embeddings (direct)\ntext-embedding-3-large\n@ 1536 dimensions\n\nROLE\n  Embed query for vector\n  search \u00b7 matches model\n  used during ingestion\n\nWhy 1536 dims?\n  Matryoshka truncation\n  matches both:\n    pdf-pipeline output\n    pmc_oa_ingest output\n  Different model = garbage\n  vector search results\n\nDirect (not NVIDIA hub)\n  -3-large not available on\n  the NVIDIA inference hub\n\nAuth: OPENAI_API_KEY",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
