      "text": "get_personalized_feed(p_user_id, p_cursor, p_limit, p_filter)\n  Cursor-paginated \u00b7 WHERE created_at < p_cursor\n  filter: 'all' | 'following'\n\n  SCORE\n    follow_boost = 1.5 if author followed else 1.0\n    specialty_match = 1.2 if post.specialty_tags &&\n                      viewer.interests else 1.0\n    recency = 1 / (1 + age_days)\n    + 0.10 \u00b7 ln(likes + 1)\n    + 0.05 \u00b7 ln(comments + 1)\n\n  Anonymisation\n    is_anonymous \u2192 'Anonymous Physician'\n    + suppresses author_specialty + avatar\n    (preserves country)\n\nget_post_with_context(p_post_id, p_user_id)\n  Single post with viewer_liked + is_following flags\n  Same anonymisation as feed\n\nget_comments_with_context(p_post_id, p_user_id, p_limit)\n  Comments + author info + viewer_liked\n  Ordered by created_at ASC (chronological)\n\ndiscover_users(p_user_id, p_specialty, p_country,\n               p_limit, p_offset)\n  Excludes self \u00b7 onboarding_complete=true\n  ORDER BY follower_count DESC, post_count DESC\n  Returns is_following flag per row",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "get_personalized_feed(p_user_id, p_cursor, p_limit, p_filter)\n  Cursor-paginated \u00b7 WHERE created_at < p_cursor\n  filter: 'all' | 'following'\n\n  SCORE\n    follow_boost = 1.5 if author followed else 1.0\n    specialty_match = 1.2 if post.specialty_tags &&\n                      viewer.interests else 1.0\n    recency = 1 / (1 + age_days)\n    + 0.10 \u00b7 ln(likes + 1)\n    + 0.05 \u00b7 ln(comments + 1)\n\n  Anonymisation\n    is_anonymous \u2192 'Anonymous Physician'\n    + suppresses author_specialty + avatar\n    (preserves country)\n\nget_post_with_context(p_post_id, p_user_id)\n  Single post with viewer_liked + is_following flags\n  Same anonymisation as feed\n\nget_comments_with_context(p_post_id, p_user_id, p_limit)\n  Comments + author info + viewer_liked\n  Ordered by created_at ASC (chronological)\n\ndiscover_users(p_user_id, p_specialty, p_country,\n               p_limit, p_offset)\n  Excludes self \u00b7 onboarding_complete=true\n  ORDER BY follower_count DESC, post_count DESC\n  Returns is_following flag per row",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
