      "text": "id          UUID PK\nresponse_id UUID FK CASCADE\nquestion_id UUID FK CASCADE\nanswer_text TEXT\n  scale value as string\n  open_text content\nanswer_options TEXT[]\n  selected option UUIDs\n  for multiple_choice\n  and multi_select\n\nINDEXES\n  response_id\n  question_id\n\nRLS\n  insert: own response only\n  read: own response OR\n        survey creator OR\n        any admin\n\nAGGREGATION (backend/surveys.py)\n  multiple_choice / multi_select\n    \u2192 option_counts dict\n  scale\n    \u2192 scale_distribution dict\n    \u2192 average_scale rounded(2)\n  open_text\n    \u2192 first 200 responses",
      "fontSize": 9,
