      "updated": 1745800000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "FastAPI app entry \u00b7 37 routes\nLimiter (slowapi) keyed by user_id\n  (Bearer JWT) \u2192 fallback IP\nTrustedHostMiddleware\n  *.onrender.com \u00b7 localhost\nCORSMiddleware\n  FRONTEND_URL \u00b7 *.vercel.app\n  allow_credentials=true\nStartup: pre-warm all clients\nCompat patch: drops langfuse\n  sdk_integration kwarg\n_msg_to_history: appends cited\n  source content to assistant\n  history for follow-up grounding",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "FastAPI app entry \u00b7 37 routes\nLimiter (slowapi) keyed by user_id\n  (Bearer JWT) \u2192 fallback IP\nTrustedHostMiddleware\n  *.onrender.com \u00b7 localhost\nCORSMiddleware\n  FRONTEND_URL \u00b7 *.vercel.app\n  allow_credentials=true\nStartup: pre-warm all clients\nCompat patch: drops langfuse\n  sdk_integration kwarg\n_msg_to_history: appends cited\n  source content to assistant\n  history for follow-up grounding",
