      "text": "Pydantic Settings \u00b7 @lru_cache\nLoads from .env (extra='ignore')\nDefaults\n  litellm_model=anthropic/\n    claude-sonnet-4-6\n  classify_model=groq/\n    llama-3.3-70b-versatile\n  embedding_model=text-\n    embedding-3-large @ 1536\n  retrieval_top_k=40\n  rerank_top_n=10\n  rrf_k=60\n  dense_weight=0.6\n  sparse_weight=0.4\n  enable_drug_retrieval=True\n  qdrant_collection='qwiva_docs'",
