      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "auth.py  (1.1 KB)\n  HTTPBearer dep \u00b7 jwt.decode HS256\n  options: require=['sub','exp']\n          verify_aud=False\n  \u2192 UserProfile(user_id=sub,\n                email=email)\n  Raises 401 on any failure\n\ndb.py  (~600 B)\n  Lazy global AsyncClient singleton\n  service key (bypasses RLS)\n  every query MUST filter by\n  user_id explicitly",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
