      "text": "TTL caches\n  _conv_list_cache \u00b7 30s TTL\n  _conv_cache \u00b7 300s TTL\n  Invalidate on mutations\n\nFunctions\n  create / list / get / update_title /\n  delete_conversation\n  append_user_message     (RPC + 3-call fallback)\n  append_assistant_message (RPC + 2-call fallback)\n  get_active_path  (RPC + suggestions merge)\n  get_siblings \u00b7 switch_branch",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "TTL caches\n  _conv_list_cache \u00b7 30s TTL\n  _conv_cache \u00b7 300s TTL\n  Invalidate on mutations\n\nFunctions\n  create / list / get / update_title /\n  delete_conversation\n  append_user_message     (RPC + 3-call fallback)\n  append_assistant_message (RPC + 2-call fallback)\n  get_active_path  (RPC + suggestions merge)\n  get_siblings \u00b7 switch_branch",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
