      "text": "require_admin() Depends\n  fetches profile \u00b7 enforces role='admin'\n\nFunctions\n  create_survey (rolls back questions on err)\n  list_surveys (active + has_responded enrich)\n  list_my_surveys (admin own drafts)\n  get_survey_detail (gather: row+questions+resp)\n  submit_response (UNIQUE enforced via 422)\n  get_results\n    aggregates by question_type\n    MC/multi \u2192 counts dict\n    scale \u2192 distribution + average\n    open_text \u2192 first 200",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "require_admin() Depends\n  fetches profile \u00b7 enforces role='admin'\n\nFunctions\n  create_survey (rolls back questions on err)\n  list_surveys (active + has_responded enrich)\n  list_my_surveys (admin own drafts)\n  get_survey_detail (gather: row+questions+resp)\n  submit_response (UNIQUE enforced via 422)\n  get_results\n    aggregates by question_type\n    MC/multi \u2192 counts dict\n    scale \u2192 distribution + average\n    open_text \u2192 first 200",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
